longer remember"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:23:37","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Say to the prophet, ‘What has the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" answered you?’ or ‘What has the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" spoken?’ "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:23:38","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But if you say, ‘The burden of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":",’ then this is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says: Because you have said, ‘The burden of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":",’ and I specifically told you not to say, ‘The burden of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":",’ "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:23:39","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will surely forget you. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Some Hb mss; other Hb mss, LXX, Syr, Vg read surely lift you up"},{"kind":"text","text":" I will throw you away from my presence —both you and the city that I gave you and your ancestors. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Some Hb mss; other Hb mss, LXX, Syr, Vg read surely lift you up"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:23:40","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will bring on you everlasting disgrace and humiliation "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 78:66","book":"Psa","chapter":78,"verse":66,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 20:11","book":"Jer","chapter":20,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" that will never be forgotten.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 78:66","book":"Psa","chapter":78,"verse":66},{"label":"Jr 20:11","book":"Jer","chapter":20,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783099445345}